{"tid":676056,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我爸是李剛]帶200g髮Gel上機被拒 馬逢國涉「撻朵」議員身份獲放行","createTime":"2018-05-24T05:26:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:56:41.000Z","uid":51271,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"61caba1a36975115778f3e2412aa5903a2a86e0c","tid":676056,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:26:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180524/58230896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230896&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=de3ddd71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58230896&h=a5278a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180524/58230896</a><br />\n<br />\n 本報接獲投訴，指立法會議員馬逢國日前離港時，手提行李中有一支200克的髮型造型啫喱。由於該支造型啫喱的容量超出100毫升的規定，安檢期間，曾有職員要求他棄置或將物件寄倉，但遭他拒絕。馬更被指曾「撻朵」表明自己為立法會議員兼揚言「搵上級過嚟同我傾」、「我識林天福(機場管理局行政總裁)」。經過多番交涉後，馬終獲「放行」，成功將該支造型啫喱手提上機。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，馬逢國日前離港，在離境大堂進行安檢時，有職員發現馬逢國的背囊疑似有金屬類的不明物品，隨即示意馬打開其背囊檢查，並發現背囊內有一支200克的髮型造型啫喱。職員隨即跟馬解釋，該支髮型造型啫喱容量超過100毫升的規定，不能手提上機，需寄倉或棄置，但馬要求「搵上級過嚟同我傾」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，另一名職員向馬再次重申，他所攜帶的髮型造型啫喱容量超過100毫升，不能手提上機，只能寄倉或棄置。但馬隨即表明自己為立法會議員，投訴人指馬曾說「我識林天福(機場管理局行政總裁)，叫話得事嘅嚟傾」。隨後再有一名較高級的職員與馬接觸，經過多番交涉後，馬終獲「放行」，成功將不合規格的造型啫喱手提上機。<br />\n<br />\n根據民航處規定，手提行李中攜帶液體、凝膠和噴霧類物品的限制是遵照國際民用航空組織的指引。香港國際機場由2007年3月21日開始，所有旅客隨身攜帶之液體、凝膠及噴霧類物品，均需以容量不超過100毫升的容器盛載。任何容量大於100毫升的容器，就算未裝滿液體、凝膠或噴霧類物品，亦不會接納。<br />\n<br />\n所有盛載液體、凝膠及噴霧類物品之容器，均應儲存於一個容量不超過一公升、並可重複密封的透明塑膠袋內，而且要確保塑膠袋完全封妥。旅客行經安檢站時，裝有容器的塑膠袋應與隨身行李分開擺放，以便進行檢查。而液體、凝膠和噴霧類物品就包括凝膠，例如髮膠，及液體與固體之混合物等。<br />\n<br />\n馬今日回應指，確曾發生帶200克造型啫喱上機一事，他承認曾與職員理論，認為該支造型啫喱實際已不足100ml，應可上機，所以據理力爭。他辯稱當時冇「撻朵」，但有觸及自己的立法會議員身份，否認有表示識林天福，澄清當時第二位處理的職員自稱是「最高級職員」，他才反駁「你唔係，最高級係林天福」。馬指最終第三位職員處理時，將他的造型啫喱再量過，過機後終放行。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527136526_a1c0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F1527136526_a1c0.jpg&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=29a0b834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180524/large/1527136526_a1c0.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n馬逢國回應事件，並展示涉事髮型造型啫喱，認為內裡實際已不足100ml。 (周智堅攝)"},{"pid":"f36eaee4ca06d9f968490dcf77189d4236bbf030","tid":676056,"uid":51105,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"咁少頭髮仲gel乜撚"},{"pid":"03aed37033f22858a48b144fd2f52106ecc1e1fc","tid":676056,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"平時佢上電視都唔覺佢有jel喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee33527b05b50ce3d14a4ac07bb536f623317e70","tid":676056,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:33:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/images/mem_1620/mfk.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fimages%2Fmem_1620%2Fmfk.jpg&d=4X0Lnw4YZQJ04v%2FiyjgTgWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=8ea299a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/images/mem_1620/mfk.jpg</a><br />\n都光晒頭，仲要gel頭？"},{"pid":"2f4708358be3b739ee5131cd113b74db82816df1","tid":676056,"uid":42909,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"無頭髮帶髪gel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿婆跑得快 一定有古怪<br />\n係我就點都check下係咪毒品黎"},{"pid":"b3fd60855404160d4bef4370f4aab3c3085a22b7","tid":676056,"uid":40839,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不嬲液體既話 無論多少都係計容器容量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2359ac1c384010f259ccb1dbd86b12e21def08","tid":676056,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"好大既官威阿，包大人"},{"pid":"dd792a430038503576a1f48ab65b3a2c01a8bc41","tid":676056,"uid":30202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"啲思維同大陸仔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf35cafcfc8309f8cd6420dbbf18a6965ce57f3","tid":676056,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20161222/large/1482412925_2608.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F1482412925_2608.jpg&h=5adafead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01d2882fb7f293937e8a9cdbad4242bf6bcfb990","tid":676056,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"又可以send 俾IATA, 但無人理"},{"pid":"705cc9747455eeef578525b1d883e201081e3c9a","tid":676056,"uid":110859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:40:32.000Z","msg":"將他的造型啫喱再量過？<br />\n請問點量？倒出來？量杯？<br />\n下次可帶唔夠100ml水入去？"},{"pid":"7e63670ee9735b492d751de4250000b88a163a53","tid":676056,"uid":34080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8737dbe28d31eb1e3a574d54b